data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: What I can see from the picture is that an adult woman is standing in front of a massive shelf on which a large number of toy sharks are placed. Those toy sharks are in the color of grey and white and look quite soft. The woman has short black hair and is wearing a black short-sleeved T-shirt and a brown vest. She is placing one of her hands on the toys. I suppose she is selling the toys to the customers who come into her shop. In the background, there is a colorful painting on the wall which is composed of a tall tree and a monkey hanging over the branch. And the light overhead is turned on. (118字)
